{"name":"黑暗语","permission":{"default":0,"UmXPyDlsSZ2Z2C5b":3},"type":"language","data":{"description":"<p>一种喉语，充满了难以发音的辅音，黑暗语起源于数千年前的古格人（Gog），那个被诅咒的国度曾扩张至整个茹尔（Rul）大陆，最终被帝国的奠基者摧毁。野兽人，邪教徒和其他寻求禁忌知识的人会学习并运用这门语言。</p>","read":false,"write":false,"speak":true},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"6ht6mf07jcs54VQS"}
{"name":"矮人语","permission":{"default":0,"UmXPyDlsSZ2Z2C5b":3},"type":"language","data":{"description":"<p>来自矮人的语言，有粗糙的声音，有着准确的词典和长的合成词。使用卢恩字母表。</p>","read":true,"write":true,"speak":true},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"KKf4LnsH6AZksjuQ"}
{"name":"通用语","permission":{"default":0,"UmXPyDlsSZ2Z2C5b":3},"type":"language","data":{"description":"<p>帝国统治领地内的主要语言，商人们为了促进交易而逐渐从过去的本地语言改良而成。拥有自己独立的字母表</p>","read":false,"write":false,"speak":true},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Qevj4xeYWb7Mmq32"}
{"name":"精灵语","permission":{"default":0,"UmXPyDlsSZ2Z2C5b":3},"type":"language","data":{"description":"<p>精灵和其他精类生物使用的语言，拥有轻柔宛如音乐的音调，极其适合唱歌和唱诗。精灵语有独特的笔迹，每个字符都会自然的衔接上前一个。</p>","read":false,"write":false,"speak":true},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"SNWaBthWBgURCpxF"}
{"name":"巨魔语","permission":{"default":0,"UmXPyDlsSZ2Z2C5b":3},"type":"language","data":{"description":"<p>精灵语有多美丽，巨魔语就有多丑陋。这种语言几乎只在巨魔和巨人间使用，听上去像是咕噜声和犬吠声的混合体。和矮人语一样使用卢恩字母表。</p>","read":false,"write":false,"speak":true},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"fYPFUuGOowrDbE24"}
{"name":"失落语言","permission":{"default":0,"UmXPyDlsSZ2Z2C5b":3},"type":"language","data":{"description":"<p>很多语言已经不再常用。GM可以介绍那些来自失落种族的语言和几乎无人热衷的语言。这些语言很可能对于理解远古的书卷和典籍有着极其重要的作用。</p>","read":false,"write":false,"speak":true},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"fpPZSIurwhYONKC4"}
{"name":"高等奥秘语","permission":{"default":0,"UmXPyDlsSZ2Z2C5b":3},"type":"language","data":{"description":"<p>知识和魔法的语言，几乎没有人使用这个语言进行对话。和通用语用相同的字母表。</p>","read":false,"write":true,"speak":false},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"pINDYdNTzMivcG6K"}
